insert into Films Values('The Lost World', 1997, 5, 'Ian Malcolm learns that there was another island before Jurassic Park, and that dinosaurs have been breeding unchecked and a group of scientists, including Malcolm''s wife, have been sent to study the them in their natural habitat. Soon they are joined by an InGen group who plan to start a new park in San Diego.')
insert into Films Values('Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl', 2003, 5, 'Captain Jack Sparrow, along with a blacksmith called Will Turner team up to stop the Black Pearl''s nefarious pirate captain, Hector Barbossa, from breaking the Aztec gold''s curse and save Elizabeth Swann.')
insert into Films Values('Harry Potter and Goblet of Fire', 2005, 5, 'Hogwarts plays host to the Tri-Wizard Tournament and Harry becomes an unwilling participant as a dark plot takes place to revive the dark wizard Voldemort.')
insert into Films Values('The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey', 2012, 5, 'Bilbo Baggins is swept up on an adventure with Gandalf the Grey and thirteen dwarves, led by Thorin Oakenshield, in order to reclaim the Dwarf Kingdom of Erebor from the fearsome dragon Smaug but before they get to the Lonely Mountain they must pass through the Goblin Caves where Bilbo will find Gollum and a his "precious".')
insert into Films Values('The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King', 2003, 5, 'Aragorn, Legolas and Gimli summon the Army of the Dead to aid Gondor in the Battle of the Pelennor Fields. Steward Denethor loses his sanity and fails to kill his son, Faramir. The Witch-King meets his end at the hands of Eowyn. Frodo and Sam venture through Shelob''s Lair in order to complete their quest. Gollum gets his just desserts.')
